        [
          "You want to check out the urban street art scene in LA and need someone who knows it the streets. The snotty members of your clan wouldn't be caught dead there. Find someone who is willing to help you out."
        ],
        [
          "You have a dream of leaving your mark somewhere in a piece that will get you noticed outside of NYC and your sire. Maybe people in court will have an idea for a place to serve as a canvas for you and inspiration for what it might be."
