          "staff_generated_concept": "You have a dream of leaving your mark somewhere in a piece that will get you noticed outside of NYC and your sire. Maybe people in court will have an idea for a place to serve as a canvas for you and inspiration for what it might be."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "LA is a lot more settled than NYC is, and it's tempting to stay somewhere where there seems to be someone in charge. Maybe consider it for a future home. If not, there are other cities, other places, and other vampires not Camarilla."
        },
